{"type":"message","id":"d2892180","parentId":"23bd975c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T05:43:59.075Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_642e151b366759d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-03\n\n## Actions\n- Installed `find-skill` and `skill-vetter` skills.\n\n## Preferences\n- All future skill installations must be audited through `skill-vetter`.\n\n## Project \"EC\" (iOS Automation Framework)\n- **WebSocket Stability**: \n    - Backend: Added active heartbeats (30s/10s) and handshake timeouts in `web_control_center/backend/main.py`.\n    - iOS Client: Implemented exponential backoff (1s-30s) for reconnect logic in `ECMAIN/ECMAIN/Core/ECBackgroundManager.m`.\n- **Mutual Watchdog**:\n    - **Logic**: ECWDA (WebDriverAgent) monitors ECMAIN on port 8089; ECMAIN monitors ECWDA on port 10088/10089.\n    - **Control**: Added \"Watchdog WDA\" (探活 WDA) toggle to both the Web Control Center dashboard and the ECMAIN iOS app home screen.\n    - **Persistence**: Used `NSUserDefaults` (Suite: `group.com.ecmain.shared`, Key: `EC_WATCHDOG_WDA_ENABLED`).\n    - **Default State**: Enabled (YES) by default unless manually toggled off. \n- **Build Progress**: Latest ECMAIN build succeeded (#1784).\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775281439073}}
